Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.60,0:02:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天絕對要說出真相
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.39,0:02:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好地向鳴唐同學道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.53,0:02:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這麼吵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.19,0:02:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這  這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.14,0:02:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我去一趟辦公室
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.38,0:02:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈途君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.07,0:02:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也算是一位思春期男性
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.47,0:03:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些這個那個事的也是沒辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.86,0:03:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然發生在三次元
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.59,0:03:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了  突然火箭就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.73,0:03:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都出了鼻血了  你還裝蒜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.64,0:03:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是Mr.鬼畜王
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.53,0:03:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是因為倒下的時候撞到鼻子了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.67,0:03:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說這是托誰的福才成這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.04,0:03:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  我只是公開了照片而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.72,0:03:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰做了些什麼可一句話都沒說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.05,0:03:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你平時品行不端才招來懷疑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.87,0:03:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.60,0:03:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.24,0:03:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實回答我  鳴唐同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.53,0:03:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈途君對你做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.47,0:03:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.53,0:03:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說吃吃吃…吃了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.73,0:03:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是真的吧  丈途
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.91,0:03:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我這不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.27,0:03:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟敢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.70,0:03:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我  拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.27,0:04:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要殺了這傢伙  再去自殺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.99,0:04:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.17,0:04:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜一下  姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.56,0:04:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡不行啊  這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.73,0:04:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不會相信的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.26,0:04:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈途不會做那樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.03,0:04:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.09,0:04:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞希老師  給我點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.59,0:04:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會證明丈途的清白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.78,0:04:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尊重學生的自主性正是閃學園的初衷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.06,0:04:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等真相大白之後再作處分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.15,0:04:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果真是那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.77,0:04:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就做好覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.78,0:04:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情鬧大了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.37,0:04:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說處罰了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.61,0:04:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的生命都有危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.01,0:04:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.12,0:05:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在弄清照片的真相之前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.53,0:05:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓別人傷你分毫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.09,0:05:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.19,0:05:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我個人討厭有罪推定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.59,0:05:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡事都想弄個究竟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.16,0:05:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.13,0:05:17.31,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能理解為女性下體
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.13,0:05:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.07,0:05:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種理所當然的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.96,0:05:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小題大作也得有個限度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36}律  快  那個算式
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.08,0:05:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3.1415926…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火箭?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.30,0:05:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你在那啊  我都沒發覺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.95,0:05:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那有記錄影像什麼的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能給我看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.53,0:05:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  好麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.31,0:05:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在正檢查新發明呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.73,0:05:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粘粘君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.37,0:05:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粘粘君?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粘粘君可是很厲害的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.30,0:06:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴿子扳手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.82,0:06:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以釋放特殊的磁力為媒介
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.96,0:06:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論什麼都可以粘在一起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.00,0:06:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粘在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.30,0:06:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合體
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.31,0:06:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合體  合體  合體  合體…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.85,0:06:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是合體
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃驚得沒話說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.29,0:06:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  這事現在都無所謂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  看來還不知道粘粘君的厲害之處呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.20,0:06:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著  Power up
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.30,0:06:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.39,0:07:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.51,0:07:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦  這下變得有趣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.94,0:07:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼  好疼  好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.98,0:07:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  完全分不開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.14,0:07:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全壞掉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開小吹音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.76,0:07:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  這到底是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.08,0:07:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  把衣服脫了試試
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.62,0:07:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我脫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.48,0:07:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要脫的是丈途
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.30,0:07:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你挺喜歡的吧  從工作角度上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.31,0:07:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快脫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.79,0:08:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你胡說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.59,0:08:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然叫丈途在眾人面前…脫衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啦  我會脫的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.37,0:08:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈途
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.91,0:08:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.37,0:08:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來必須得修理機器了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.39,0:08:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候才能修好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.10,0:08:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天知道  或許明天或許明年
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.42,0:08:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.38,0:08:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放鬆點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.09,0:08:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管發生什麼事我都不會打擾的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.74,0:08:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼會有什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.20,0:08:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會有什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能放鬆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.91,0:08:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話  話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.50,0:08:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次把女生帶進房間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妄想不能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.44,0:09:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變更原有播放計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.17,0:09:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來播出芥川丈途的妄想劇場
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.93,0:09:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.54,0:09:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.06,0:09:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這  這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.28,0:09:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說現在不是考慮這個的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.04,0:09:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不正是向鳴唐同學道歉的好機會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.83,0:09:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴  鳴  鳴唐同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,癡漢列車  奈留惠  宣傳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,資  資料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.04,0:09:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是關於列車小說的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.42,0:09:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好危險
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.62,0:09:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的房間好危險
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直是工口火藥庫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.97,0:09:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您拜託的資料送來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.75,0:10:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是騷擾傳真
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.53,0:10:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能稍稍打掃下房間麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.84,0:10:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.72,0:10:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.97,0:10:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人  冷靜一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.49,0:10:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能讓小吹音待在那賊窩裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.48,0:10:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,資料有好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.74,0:10:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是嗎  也不會很多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.49,0:10:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小說家很厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.38,0:10:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒那樣的事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.66,0:10:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  這樣終於能冷靜地對話了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.52,0:10:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以練習嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.36,0:10:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,練習?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.37,0:10:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個像標誌一樣的是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.18,0:10:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼特殊的單簧管嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.09,0:11:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  只是有點在意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想說的話也沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是重要的人送給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.44,0:11:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重  重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.99,0:11:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  爸爸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.11,0:11:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  有必要特意現在練習嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.99,0:11:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單簧管是一天都不能停止練習的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.98,0:11:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.04,0:11:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是也會有各種情況不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.18,0:11:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如累了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.32,0:11:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候就應該好好放鬆一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.89,0:11:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微休息也不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.24,0:11:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是這樣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.64,0:11:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.54,0:11:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謠  謠江同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.57,0:12:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情變得很糟糕了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.24,0:12:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身邊也有人在議論
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.09,0:12:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明丈途同學不會是這種人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.14,0:12:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謠江同學  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.63,0:12:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢  丈途同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.66,0:12:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.43,0:12:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  你和其他人在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.37,0:12:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒  沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.03,0:12:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  編輯差不多要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.62,0:12:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  下次再聊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.00,0:12:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  再見！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.59,0:12:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來我為什麼要說謊呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.42,0:12:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  還真是厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.28,0:12:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這聲音彷彿淨化了心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.59,0:13:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打擾你了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.95,0:13:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.32,0:13:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.87,0:13:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吹不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.00,0:13:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.13,0:13:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把我當成石頭或傢俱就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.09,0:13:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.75,0:13:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.69,0:13:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不存在  不存在！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.23,0:13:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈途遇到了這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.59,0:13:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我卻什麼都做不了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.13,0:13:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好好練習就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.00,0:13:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴唐同學  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你說說…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡著了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都這麼晚了  鳴唐同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.15,0:14:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原稿  把原稿謄清
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.65,0:14:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要看多餘的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.85,0:14:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不到的東西是不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.70,0:14:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能會看到！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.40,0:14:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發出風箱般細細的鼻息聲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.42,0:14:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是色慾與激情相互交織
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.13,0:14:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充滿情慾的吶喊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.69,0:14:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像猛然站起的一隻野獸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.42,0:14:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散發著黑亮光芒  充滿淫慾的他…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.73,0:14:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36}色慾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.79,0:14:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激情  野獸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.18,0:14:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淫慾  閃閃發光…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.56,0:14:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有看  沒有看！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.31,0:14:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以原諒我！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.75,0:15:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起對不起對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.75,0:15:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36}閃閃發光…閃閃發光…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.46,0:15:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃閃發光…閃閃發光…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.95,0:15:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起對不起對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.33,0:15:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次變更播放計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.97,0:15:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來播出芥川丈途的妄想劇場
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜晚的Touchdown
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.05,0:15:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  再來再來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.31,0:15:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.98,0:15:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修理完成了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.28,0:15:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快醒醒  鳴唐同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的修好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.81,0:15:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你竟然不相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.08,0:15:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說了沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.27,0:15:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粘粘君·改
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.50,0:16:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36}結果還是沒好好說上話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.69,0:16:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不僅僅是修好了哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.48,0:16:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點遺憾  但也沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.17,0:16:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的有效範圍…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.37,0:16:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了  快點開始啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.34,0:16:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.31,0:16:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  Switch on
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.32,0:16:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看那個！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.89,0:17:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個又壞掉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.60,0:17:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈途
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.60,0:17:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36}小吹音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.98,0:17:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得越來越混亂了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.52,0:17:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴唐同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.52,0:17:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  吹音的單簧管
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.83,0:17:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放手  這樣下去你也會被…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.49,0:17:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死也別放手  不然就殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.97,0:17:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.96,0:17:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放手！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別放手！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.99,0:18:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.17,0:18:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛  沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.60,0:18:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不痛  不痛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.96,0:18:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這很爽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.56,0:18:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很…痛  很痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.22,0:18:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻  嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.51,0:18:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻  嘿咻…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.98,0:19:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個  給你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.30,0:19:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幫我救了它呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.03,0:19:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是鳴唐同學很重要的單簧管啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.03,0:19:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有話想對你說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.85,0:19:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈途
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.49,0:19:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧  小吹音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.94,0:19:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他保護了我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.92,0:19:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那些照片是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.04,0:19:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.49,0:19:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  丈途只是去保護她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.78,0:19:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.42,0:19:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不承認這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.40,0:19:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天我會抓住你的尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情解決了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.95,0:19:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  一開始把這段錄像放出來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.25,0:20:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不會鬧成這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.06,0:20:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在調查你的時候引起了我的興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.48,0:20:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然用鼻血把我的機器全毀了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太棒了  超級變態啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.19,0:20:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣誇我一點也高興不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.84,0:20:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  讓我解剖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.14,0:20:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下  下次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.94,0:20:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了  解剖什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.41,0:20:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴  鳴唐同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.89,0:20:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.53,0:20:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.85,0:20:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛你要和我說的事  是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.73,0:20:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多事…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.27,0:20:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如簧片的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.84,0:20:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  我不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.31,0:21:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候肚子很餓  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.55,0:21:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  我能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.72,0:21:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.43,0:21:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像那樣一個拼盡全力的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.69,0:21:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不可能會吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.37,0:21:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吹音誤會了  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.11,0:21:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.90,0:21:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:21:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴唐同學一直在這裡練習
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.74,0:22:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真讓人心情舒暢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.45,0:22:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像心靈深處被溫暖了一樣

